{"tid":1633510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Financial Times: 有四分一警察公餘參加示威遊行","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:51:49.000Z","uid":129134,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7db52d50706f1f799d4bab86305c9cf243d0750e","tid":1633510,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"One senior police official says privately that as many as a quarter of his officers are joining peaceful protests in their spare time. Hated as it is right now, the Hong Kong police force is made up of Cantonese-speaking locals. Faced with a Mandarin-speaking occupying army from the north, many officers would choose to join the rebellion.<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/12119746-e67d-11e9-b112-9624ec9edc59\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F12119746-e67d-11e9-b112-9624ec9edc59&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=ec17549b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/12119746-e67d-11e9-b112-9624ec9edc59</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致所有mon po狗：<br />\n<br />\n點解你地咁多人資料上左老豆搵仔？<br />\n<br />\n點解明明朋友都未必知你老豆老母叫咩名，但老豆搵仔會乜資料都有齊？<br />\n<br />\n點解謝振中搞女督察同成家搞緊移民會爆左出黎？<br />\n<br />\n點解開槍射學生左胸個差佬，會秒速比警務署爆比法庭叫曾家輝？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你地身邊每一個都有機會係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地每一個都係condom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnd btw 藍衫筆OT費都得一兩萬上限<br />\n白衫輕輕鬆鬆過十萬<br />\n仲有PPRB班垃圾坐冷氣房出Facebook Post<br />\n都個個月十幾萬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放下屠刀立地成佛<br />\n1. 篤灰 2. 離開警隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6d226190492d61333d6bec239382064f5a9e04","tid":1633510,"uid":204872,"like":1,"dislike":